page.title: 09EDUCATION-ECOLOGY
page.content:
A man called Mr. Till did many good things for the village of Eynsford. It was his idea to plant trees set out as an acrostic at Bower Lane. Anthony Roper school was built to replace the old Eynsford school in Bower Lane and the Farningham Church of England school. So our trees are planted to repeat the message.
M Mountain Ash B Birch Y Yellow Birch E Elm
S Sycamore W Whitebeam O Oak I Indian Bean Tree N Norway Maple S Sycamore E Elm
We all do our best to take good care of our enviroment.
